f:["$","$L44",null,{"districtName":"Coimbatore","serviceLabel":"Airport Taxi","faqs":[{"question":"What is the starting fare for airport taxi in Coimbatore?","answer":"The starting fare for airport taxi in Coimbatore is ₹13/km for a hatchback. Sedan rates start at ₹14/km, SUV at ₹14/km, and Innova Crysta at ₹14/km. All fares include driver allowance, toll charges, and GST with no hidden costs."},{"question":"How do I book a airport taxi from Coimbatore?","answer":"You can book a airport taxi from Coimbatore instantly on OneWayTaxi.ai. Simply enter your pickup location, destination, date, and time. You'll get an instant fare estimate. You can also call us 24/7 at +91 81244 76010 for immediate booking."},{"question":"Is airport taxi from Coimbatore available 24/7?","answer":"Yes, our airport taxi from Coimbatore is available 24 hours a day, 7 days a week — including holidays and late nights. You can book at any time through our website or by calling our support team."},{"question":"What types of vehicles are available for airport taxi in Coimbatore?","answer":"We offer 5 vehicle types for airport taxi in Coimbatore: Mini/Hatchback (4 seats, ₹13/km), Sedan like Etios/Dzire (4 seats, ₹14/km), SUV/Innova (7 seats, ₹14/km), Innova Crysta (7 seats, ₹14/km), and Tempo Traveller (12 seats, ₹19/km)."},{"question":"Are there any hidden charges for Coimbatore airport taxi?","answer":"No, absolutely not. Our Coimbatore airport taxi fares are fully transparent and include all costs — driver bata, toll charges, permit fees, and GST. The fare you see at booking is the fare you pay. There are no surge charges, no night charges, and no return-trip charges."},{"question":"What is the fare from Coimbatore to Chennai by airport taxi?","answer":"The airport taxi fare from Coimbatore to Chennai starts at approximately ₹7070 for a hatchback. The distance is about 505 km. Sedan fare would be around ₹7070, and SUV around ₹7070. Book now for exact pricing."},{"question":"Do Coimbatore airport taxi drivers track flight delays?","answer":"Yes, our Coimbatore airport taxi drivers actively monitor flight arrival times. If your flight is delayed, your driver will adjust pickup time automatically at no extra charge. We recommend booking at least 2 hours before your desired departure time for outgoing flights."},{"question":"Is it safe to book airport taxi in Coimbatore with OneWayTaxi.ai?","answer":"Absolutely. All our Coimbatore airport taxi drivers are professionally trained, background-verified, and carry valid licenses. Our vehicles are GPS-tracked in real-time, regularly serviced, and fully insured. We have served over 50,000 happy customers across South India with a 4.8-star average rating."},{"question":"What payment methods are accepted for Coimbatore airport taxi?","answer":"We accept multiple payment methods for Coimbatore airport taxi: Cash, UPI (Google Pay, PhonePe, Paytm), credit cards, debit cards, and net banking. You can pay the driver directly in cash or via UPI at the end of your trip. No advance payment is required for booking."},{"question":"Can I cancel my Coimbatore airport taxi booking?","answer":"Yes, you can cancel your Coimbatore airport taxi booking free of charge up to 2 hours before the scheduled pickup time. Cancellations within 2 hours may attract a nominal cancellation fee. Contact our 24/7 support at +91 81244 76010 for cancellations or rescheduling."},{"question":"How much does a taxi from Coimbatore to Bangalore cost?","answer":"A one-way taxi from Coimbatore to Bangalore costs approximately ₹5110 for a hatchback (365 km). Sedan fare: ~₹5110, SUV: ~₹6935. All fares include toll, driver bata, and GST."}]}]
